comment: Mahinmi (IND) makes contact with Walker (CHA) that affects his RSBQ on the drive to the basket.
Batum (CHA) maintains a legal guarding position on the driving shot attempt by Mahinmi (IND) and any contact is incidental.
Zeller (CHA) sets the screen on Hill (IND) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Walker (CHA) maintains a legal guarding position on George's (IND) post move and shot attempt.
Mahinmi (IND) maintains a legal guarding position on Walker's (CHA) drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Lamb (CHA) cleanly strips the ball from George (IND).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Lamb (CHA) prior to going OOB was confirmed.
Walker (CHA) is retreating and maintains a legal guarding position on Ellis' (IND) drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Hill (IND) makes incidental contact with Batum (CHA) that does not affect his RSBQ.
Batum (CHA) and George (IND) briefly engage and separate during the inbounds play.
